home.1: Hello. My name is Kae Saetern, pronounced kay-say-turn. I am full-stack software engineer based in the tech hub of San Francisco, CA. After nearly a decade in education, program management, and business operations, I made a full switch to tech in 2024 with Genentech. There I launched and landed a GMP-compliant workflow-guided application that continues to be rolled out and expanded throughout the South San Francisco site to this day.
